Ingredients:
10g   olive oil
200g  beef mince      Southside Farmer's Market
100g  carrot
100g  onion
200g  tomato sauce    Passata
5g    oregano

Preparation:
Chop the onion.
Grate the carrot.
Crush oregano if it is in the leaf form.

Cooking:
Turn on stove to medium heat.
Put oil into pot. Wait until it spreads.
Put beef into pot. Wait until it is browned. Flip beef. Wait until it is browned.
Put onion into pot. Wait until it is soft.
Turn off stove.
Put sauce into pot. Wait until it is heated through.
